page.title: 17MY DAY
page.content: I woke up at 8.00am this morning and went down stairs. I got dressed into my school clothes and had my breakfast.I sat down to watch TVAM. Ann Diamond was on with some other people but I didn't find it very interesting so I went out in the kichen to pack my bag.It was coming up to 8.50am now so I went to school. To start the day we did Maths English and some reading. Then it was playtime. After play we did some work on the computer until dinner time. At dinner time I washed my hands and went in for dinner. We had sausages, mashed potatoes and baked beans. For pudding we had apple crumble.During the afternoon we did some painting. At 3.30pm we went home and I played badminton until 6pm.Then I watched TV until my bedtime at 9pm.
